        'Imperial Guard: fixed 10 infantry units (Infantry Squad, Mechanised Infantry, Platoon Command Squad, Company Command Squad, Special Weapon Squad, Veterans, Stormtroopers, Stormtrooper Command Squad, Rough Riders, Conscript Infantry Platoon) — the Grenade launcher option was selectable but both profiles (Frag grenade: 24" Assault 1 S4 AP0 D1 Explosive; Krak grenade: 24" Assault 1 S6 AP-2 D1) were missing. Both profiles now appear on the unit card.',
